plot a graph
r ggplot(zebra, aes(skull_length , tooth_p1_length)) + geom_point(size = 3 , colour = "coral")

making the model

model1 <- lm(tooth_p1_length ~ skull_length, data = zebra)

checking the assumptions

autoplot(model1, smooth.colour = NA)

anova(model1)
